scilube.imglib2

ProcessorType

object ProcessorType extends Enumeration

Enumeration of the different types of ImageJ ij.process.ImageProcessors. You can get the correct type using:

val imageProcessor: ImageProcessor = // ...
val processorType = ProcessorType.get(imageProcessor)
